### QuizMonitor API - Authentication & Users Test Requests
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7158
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health
Accept: application/json

### Database Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/health/db
Accept: application/json

###
### ========== AUTHENTICATION ==========
###

### Register - Student
# @name register
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student1@example.com",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd123",
  "fullName": "Ahmed Hassan",
  "role": "Student",
  "phoneNumber": "01012345678"
}

### Register - Instructor
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "instructor1@example.com",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd123",
  "fullName": "Dr. Mohamed Ali",
  "role": "Instructor",
  "phoneNumber": "01198765432"
}


### Register - Instructor
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "noha@example.com",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd123",
  "fullName": "Dr. noha yehia",
  "role": "Instructor",
  "phoneNumber": "01198765438"
}

### Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "noha@example.com",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd123"
}

### Refresh Token
# @name refresh
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{login.response.body.refreshToken}}"
}

###
### ========== USERS ==========
###

### Get Current User Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### ========== ERROR CASES ==========
###

### Register - Invalid Role
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd123",
  "fullName": "Test User",
  "role": "invalid_role",
  "phoneNumber": "01012345678"
}

### Register - Duplicate Email
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student1@example.com",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd123",
  "fullName": "Duplicate User",
  "role": "student",
  "phoneNumber": "01012345678"
}

### Login - Wrong Password
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "student1@example.com",
  "password": "WrongPassword"
}

### Login - Non-existent User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nonexistent@example.com",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd123"
}

### Get Profile - No Token (Should return 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me
Accept: application/json

### Get Profile - Invalid Token (Should return 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token_here

### Refresh Token - Invalid Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "invalid_refresh_token"
}
